snippet.title: Supersonic Rhyme Chamber - VR Rap & Rhythm Game - Story Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
From No Static Games, Supersonic Rhyme Chamber (aka SRC) is a VR rap & rhythm game where music has been outlawed and you must use your MC skills and magic morphing microphone to bring music back to the people of Planet Moondo!

For updates on our game dev journey, be sure to subscribe and follow us on Twitter: @NoStaticGames
